reviewText: This movie is hilarious and entertaining. Ambra Angiolini steals the movie with her beauty and acting. Enrico Brignano is a very good actor also.

Saw this movie on an international flight and loved it - clever, witty, fun, and a little silly.  Didn't realize, however, that I wouldn't be able to get english subtitles.  Italian subtitles on an italian movie doesn't help me much :(
